# kitconcept.core

Core setup for kitconcept GmbH distributions built on top of Plone

## Features

TODO: List our awesome features

## Installation

Install kitconcept.core with uv.

```shell
uv add kitconcept.core
```

Create the Plone site.

```shell
make create-site
```

